Five years ago today this beauty and I tied the knot. Since then, she’s turned our house into a home, hand made the most beautiful, perfect little boy and continues to make my life brighter and better on a daily basis. You’re the very best one, @jennywade, and I’m so grateful you’re my wife. Happy Anniversary ❤️
And that’s a wrap on the Non-Evil Twin pilot! This one was an absolute blast from start to finish. Great peeps, big laughs, good times. Fingers crossed it’s only the beginning!
Happy Mother’s Day to the best to have ever done it, @jennywade. If excelling at being a mom was an Olympic sport you would win the gold and the silver and the bronze. We love you so much. ❤️❤️

Treat was a special guy. He had a big smile, even bigger heart and he loved to laugh. He was a joy to be around. I’m grateful for the time we spent together and that I was able to call him a friend. He will be greatly missed.

More (pre-strike) self-tape bts. It’s important to have a reader that keeps you engaged and humble. Very, very humble.

Happy Birthday to the people’s champion, @jennywade! From the moment you arrived on the scene, you have rocked the very hardest. You’re impossibly cool, infinitely patient and thoroughly awesome. You > the rest. I love you. We love you. Here’s to many more years of wearing matching Canadian tuxedos together.

Congratulations to my favorite multi-hyphenate, @hilarieburton (Author-Actor-Witch) on the release of her new book, Grimoire Girl. Get yourself a copy and kick off spooky season right! Way to go, Hil!! 🧙‍♀️
